<!-- Game Controls Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BASIC CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move character / Select the monster to transform into (for rue) / Select color of magic (left/right) and the effect of magic (up/down) (for mint) / Move cursor / Select files in the save screen:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad or Left Analog Stick</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Confirm action / Talk / Execute / Normal attack:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Normal attack or monster's special attack (for Rue) / Magic attack (for Mint):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Jump / Cancel action:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Open transformation menu (menu ring) to select a monster (for Rue) / Open magic menu (menu ring) to select magic (for Mint):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; In certain locations, the view can be rotated counterclockwise / On the save screen this button also switches between memory card slots:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; In certain locations, the view can be rotated clockwise / On the save screen this button also switches between memory card slots:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; In game menu:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
        &nbsp;</td>
	 </tr>
	</table>
